duties_responsibilities.duty: Provide patient care in an acute care setting, following established protocols and procedures.
Utilize medical terminology and critical thinking to assess and respond to patient needs in emergency situations.
Collaborate with the healthcare team to ensure comprehensive and compassionate care for all patients.
Demonstrate attention to detail and accuracy in all nursing activities and documentation.

education_certification.credential: Bachelor's degree in Nursing (Master's degree preferred)
Active RN license in the state of practice
